## Architecture Summary

Mobius is a local-first PWA (Progressive Web App) deployed on Vercel Hobby plan.

- **Frontend**: single `index.html` / `commands.js` chat interface
- **Backend**: Vercel serverless functions (`api/`) — consolidated to 4 functions: Identity, Intelligence, Memory, Services
- **Local server**: `server.js` (Node.js, localhost:3000) proxies `/api/*` to Vercel; auto-starts via `MobiusServer.vbs`
- **AI routing**: Groq default → Flash-Lite (complex text) → Gemini Flash (vision) → Mistral Codestral (code)
- **Local AI**: Ollama (Intel Arc via IPEX-LLM) on desktop — `qwen2.5-coder:7b` and `deepseek-r1:7b`
- **Storage**: Supabase (knowledge, sessions, model_config, sync_queue tables)
- **Sync**: Google (personal/family/work accounts) + Dropbox OAuth

