## Key Decisions & Notes

- **Governing principle**: Mobius orchestrates, AI only proposes — AI never writes to filesystem, never commits to GitHub autonomously
- **Local where possible**: Ollama on desktop, WebLLM/WebGPU on mobile; cloud APIs are fallback
- **One codebase** runs locally on all devices; Vercel is cloud API gateway only
- **Vercel Hobby 12-function limit** — must stay at or below current consolidation
- **MOBIUS_CONTEXT.md** is the persistent knowledge anchor for all AI calls — keep it updated after every significant change

